### Tech Stack (For Your Reference, Not the Designer's)

- React 18.3 + Vite 6.4 (SPA, not Next.js)
- Tailwind CSS v4 (config in CSS via `@theme inline`, no `tailwind.config.js`)
- shadcn/ui (new-york style, neutral base)
- Radix UI primitives
- lucide-react icons
- Storybook 9.1 + Chromatic (viewports: 375, 768, 1280)
- react-hook-form + zod for forms
- Apollo Client for GraphQL
- Path alias: `@/*` maps to `./src/*`
- Class merging: `cn()` from `@/lib/utils`

